<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset = "utf-8">

    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="../images/favicon3/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="../images/favicon3/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="../images/favicon3/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="../images/favicon3/site.webmanifest">
    <link rel="mask-icon" href="../images/favicon3/safari-pinned-tab.svg" color="#008080">
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#00aba9">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:900" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Spectral" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cormorant" rel="stylesheet">
    <title> Drivers - Population Advertisements </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href = "../css/driverStyle.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    {{> header}}

    <div id="showcase">
      <div class = "textBox">
        <h1> Create your own schedule. </h1>
        <h1> Apply today. </h1>
        <div class = "buttonClass">
          <a href="/signUp" class="button"> <b> Apply Now </b> </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "headerImage">
      <div class = "imgBox">
          <img src="../images/driverPage/headBanner.jpg" >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "headerSmall">
      <div> </div>
    </div>

    <div id = "headerContent1">
      <div class = "headline">
        <h2> <b> We make it easy on you. Don't worry about anything except driving your daily routes while earning cash. </b> </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "box">
      <div class = "imgBox">
          <img src="../images/driverPage/driverImage3.jpg" >
      </div>
      <div class = "content">
        <h2> Limitless Earnings </h2>
        <p> There is no limit to how much you can earn. It is our duty to ensure that our drivers' experience a smooth journey and earn their fair amount of pay.  </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id = "headerContent2">
      <div class = "headline">
        <h2> <b> The Process </b> </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "row">
      <div class = "column">
        <div class = "card">
          <img src="../images/driverPage/howTo1.png" alt="asset1" class = "image" style="width:100%">
          <div class = "container">
            <h3> Step 1 </h3>
            <p> Apply to become a driver. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "column">
        <div class = "card">
          <img src="../images/driverPage/howTo2.png" alt="asset2" class = "image" style="width:100%">
          <div class = "container">
            <h3> Step 2 </h3>
            <p> Install our sign on your car. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "column">
        <div class = "card">
          <img src="../images/driverPage/howTo3.png" alt="asset3" class = "image" style="width:100%">
          <div class = "container">
            <h3> Step 3 </h3>
            <p> Earn for every mile driven. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id = "headerContent2">
      <div class = "headline">
        <h2> <b> Are you Eligible? </b> </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "row1">
      <div class = "column1">
        <div class = "card1">
          <div class = "container1">
            <h3> Requirements </h3>
            <div class = "listContainer">
              <ul>
                <li> 18 years or older</li>
                <li> Own a car compatible with sign</li>
                <li> Drive 300 miles per month</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "column1">
        <div class = "card1">
          <div class = "container1">
            <h3> Documents </h3>
            <div class = "listContainer">
              <ul>
                <li> Valid drivers license</li>
                <li> Proof of insurance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "column1">
        <div class = "card1">
          <div class = "container1">
            <h3> Sign Up </h3>
            <div class = "listContainer">
              <ul>
                <li> Provide valid information</li>
                <li> Determine if your car is compatible with our signs</li>
                <li> Agree to our terms and conditions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "box2">
      <div class = "content2">
        <h2> Apply Now or Learn More </h2>
        <p> We hope to work with you soon. </p>
        <p> <a href="/signUp" class="button"> <b> Apply Now </b> </a> </p>
        <p> <a href="/contact" class="button"> <b> Learn More </b> </a> </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
  </body>
</html>
